title: GET_CALMING_QUAD_DAMPENING

0xB0E3A058// GetCalmingQuadDampening
BOOL GET_CALMING_QUAD_DAMPENING(int waterQuad, float* calmingQuadDampening);Parameters:waterQuad: The calming quad indexcalmingQuadDampening: Returns: Returns true on success. Dampening value is undefined on failureExamples:Lualocal success, dampening = GetCalmingQuadDampening(1)
